<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>﴿إِنّا أَعْطَيْناكَ الْكَوْثَرَ <span class="c2">(١)</span> فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَاِنْحَرْ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> إِنَّ شانِئَكَ هُوَ الْأَبْتَرُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>﴾<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>